al causes:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\",\n    \"node_memory_usage_rate\",\n    \"io_util\",\n    \"node_filesystem_usage_rate\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node memory availability dropped significantly, potentially indicating resource exhaustion.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Drop in node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes from 9733824512.0 to 8149481472.0 during fault period.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Client error ratio and error ratio spikes in cartservice-1, indicating potential service error or overload.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio and error_ratio fault_p99 rose to 14.05.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv\",\n      \"reason\": \"IO utilization increased, potentially indicating database IO pressure.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"io_util metric increased during fault period.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased rrt_max observed, suggesting potential service latency due to overload.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max rose to 5402.78.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nThese hypotheses point to multiple domains of issues including node resource constraints, service errors, and database IO bottlenecks. Further investigation into each specific area is recommended to pinpoint the exact root cause.", "trace_analysis_findings": "I've collected trace data related to the anomaly from 2025-06-06T21:10:18Z to 2025-06-06T21:22:18Z. Below are the findings from the data:\n\n### Detected Trace Anomalies:\n1. **Cart Service Anomalies:**\n   - `checkoutservice->cartservice`: \n     - Empty Cart (`POST /hipstershop.CartService/EmptyCart`): Normal Avg Duration: 2258.79ms, Anomaly Avg Duration: 33052.33ms\n     - Get Cart (`POST /hipstershop.CartService/Ge